OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer Cat Dinneny
OL,9,FThere are fears that more patients
OL,10,Fcould have died at the hands of a
OL,11,Frogue breast surgeon.
OL,13,FThe deaths of two more women will be
OL,14,Finvestigated by the coroner, who is
OL,15,Fcurrently examining whether 62 women
OL,16,Fdied as a result of their treatment by
OL,17,FIan Paterson.
