OL,3,CMore deaths investigated over fears
OL,4,Cthey could be linked to surgeon Ian
OL,5,CPaterson
OL,7,FPaterson - who worked at hospitals
OL,8,Facross Birmingham and Solihull - is
OL,9,Fcurrently serving a 20-year jail
OL,10,Fsentence after he was found guilty of
OL,11,F17 counts of wounding patients with
OL,12,Fintent, against ten victims, in 2017.
OL,14,FThe inquests into the deaths of his
OL,15,Fpatients started in October last year
OL,16,Fand will determine whether Paterson's
OL,17,Fmalpractice - namely his 'cleavage-
OL,18,Fsparing mastectomy' which left some
OL,19,Fbreast tissue behind - is to blame for
OL,20,Ftheir deaths.
