OL,5,CPaterson
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, it was announced that two
OL,8,Fmore women, Judith Ingham and Pearl
OL,9,FTatlow, will have their deaths
OL,10,Fexamined.
OL,12,FMs Ingham died in March 2022, and Ms
OL,13,FTatlow died in July that year. Their
OL,14,Finquests will be opened on June 3,
OL,15,Fbefore the inquest of Elaine Morris,
OL,16,Fwho died in 2002, resumes.
